Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def

This package contains the IAeBpelDefWriter interface for serializing specific AeBaseDef object subclasses and the default impls.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeBpelDefWriter Interface for working with AeDef object serializers.
IAeWriterDefVisitor A simple extension to the def visitor that exposes the ability to get a resulting Element from the visitor once the visit is complete.
IAeWriterDefVisitorFactory A factory interface for creating writer def visitors.
 

Class Summary
AeBPWSWriterVisitor An implementation of a writer visitor for bpel4ws 1.1.
AeDispatchWriter Generic writer class for serializing AeDef objects.
AeWriterVisitor Impl of the def visitor that serializes the def to a DOM.
AeWSBPELAbstractProcessWriterVisitor A WS-BPEL 2.0 Abstract Process implementation of a writer visitor.
AeWSBPELWriterVisitor A WS-BPEL 2.0 implementation of a writer visitor.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def Description

This package contains the IAeBpelDefWriter interface for serializing specific AeBaseDef object subclasses and the default impls.
